name: GU Gingerade Gel
description: The smooth heat of ginger helps keep you fired up. An engineered blend of carbohydrates (70-80% maltodextrin and 30-20% fructose) is easy to digest and provides a long-lasting surge of energy.Ingredients: Maltodextrin, water, fructose, leucine, citric acid, sodium citrate, natural flavor, sea salt, potassium citrate, calcium carbonate, valine, laic acid, gellan gum, isoleucine, sunflower oil, sodium benzoate (preservative), potassium sorbate (preservative).Complex and simple carbs are optimized for rapid absorption and energy accessibility.
